# Fix News API 500 Error

The user is experiencing a 500 Interner Server Error when fetching news.
The cause is a missing Sequelize association between `News` and `User` models, while the controller tries to `include` User as `author`.

## Proposed Changes

### Backend
#### [MODIFY] [models/news.js](file:///c:/Users/HPPAVILION/Documents/Cusor/Cafe_app/my-app/backend/models/news.js)
- Add association: `News.belongsTo(User, { foreignKey: 'created_by', as: 'author' });`
- Requires importing `User`.

#### [MODIFY] [Frontend/src/stores/orderStore.js](file:///c:/Users/HPPAVILION/Documents/Cusor/Cafe_app/my-app/Frontend/src/stores/orderStore.js)
